The paper discusses the problems in current crisis response operations and compares different crisis response systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category, as it deals with the interaction between humans and technology in crisis response. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of technology and artificial intelligence in crisis response, which makes the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories likely as well.
